{"word":"ἐπιμαίνομαι","slug":"ἐπιμαίνομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιμαίνομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2 <el>-εμάνην</el>) (<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> <el>-εμηνάμην</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-μέμηνα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be mad after, dote upon</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to be mad, to rage</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to attack furiously</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}